{"title":"走在堤上——建军节里的回忆","authors":["赵伟"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":8,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在堤上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——建军节里的回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涨洪水的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又来到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的堤坝上还留着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些深深的脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤外的涛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧奔腾不息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个赶驴的小孩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱着童谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从堤上走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的曲子在这个傍晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成一片夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隆重地覆盖着你那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深的脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跪下身默默地捧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷彩鞋的味道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香飘四溢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红背心和糊满泥浆的脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在脚印的深处晃动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血肉穿过铁网在木桩上盛开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地落在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咆哮的江面上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不沉溺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着堤坝走去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见所有的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在呼喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那沿江两岸的喊声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与堤坝和江水一同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸向遥远的天边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地藏在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大大小小的脚印里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叠筑起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤——变成了碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水——变成了旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远方的四合院里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你家的鸡下了一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双黄蛋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲给你留着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小吃双黄蛋长大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以身体才这般结实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以你才能——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住那一泻千里的江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只从小和你长大的狗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从早到晚站在村头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今我再来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你没有与我同行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤内堤外一片安宁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄炊烟四起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶驴的小孩已经回家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跪在堤下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跪在夕阳的风里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找你的红背心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找你糊满泥浆的脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有雄性的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涨洪水的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我又来到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤上堤下一片静谧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年的喊声歌声号声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由远而近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年的汗水泪水江水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难解难分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我分明知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤——变成了碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水——变成了旗"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}